{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534493849&di=9c8c93c39bfa8ff9d9ed1002cb0a3e23&src=http%3A%2F%2Fg.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F58ee3d6d55fbb2fbcd26cd3e474a20a44623dc89.jpg","summary":"黑河学院(Heihe University)坐落在国家首批沿边开放城市——黑河市，与素有“大学城”美誉的俄罗斯布拉戈维申斯克市隔江相望，是中俄边境线上中国境内唯一一所省属普通高等本科院校,。学校创办于1958年，历经黑河师范专科学校、齐齐哈尔大学黑河分校等发展阶段。2004年5月晋升为本科院校。截至2016年8月，学校占地面积53.67万平方米，校舍建筑面积24.36万平方米，固定资产总值3.65亿元；教学科研仪器设备值8540.28万元。设二级学院(部)14个，开设36个本科专业；有教职工779人，其中专任教师525人，博士9人，硕士364人。","tags":["综合类","本科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"1958","所在地区":"黑龙江省黑河市学院路1号","院校隶属":"黑龙江省"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493849&di=96f42365918f9f31cabd892b9f54549c&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3684771010%2C875167609%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493849&di=c11861da956159b5a63157d93d9f6944&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3665673665%2C4180238760%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493849&di=ad991acc596c4f81be181f3b92d3c8e7&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3595290736%2C3713185236%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493849&di=ccba0dd27560fc1020c9e47cce214f01&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D2741376787%2C2673114617%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493849&di=e1af8e06c5cf7111c7ef6c6511831420&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3686432764%2C856665901%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=15344